# CVE-2026-34077 — turbo-stream 2.4.1 (React Router/Remix single-fetch DoS).
# Fixed only in turbo-stream 3.0.0, but Remix 2.17.x pins turbo-stream to
# exactly 2.4.1: 3.0.0 is a breaking API change (binary streams) that throws
# "input must be an ArrayBuffer/ArrayBufferView" inside Remix's single-fetch
# serializer and takes down dashboard SSR app-wide. There is no Remix-2.17-
# compatible patched release (npm jumps 2.4.1 → 3.0.0), so the override is
# incompatible with the framework. Suppress until the dashboard migrates to
# React Router v7 (which vendors turbo-stream 3.x natively).
CVE-2026-34077
